{"tid":2420933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK Watch 創辦人：香港人唔可以圍埋喺China Town、Hong Kong Town","createTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:45:14.000Z","uid":91721,"like":133,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"14323f03180cd8ab8549369ea47c49c6ad839eb0","tid":2420933,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"「港版國安法」令各國為港人趟開移民大門，每道門、每艘艇也是血汗換來的結果。有份在背後為港人奔走、88年移居加拿大的港人Aileen Calverley接受《蘋果》訪問時透露，香港問題最初登不上國際舞台，直至中大、理大兩場重要戰役，始令多國目光投向香港予以支援。她寄語港人離鄉後積極融入當地社會，在異地投票甚至參選做議員，盡力為香港族群說話...<br />\n<br />\n外國最初對港關注度明顯不高，她舉例指，香港監察2018年曾到聯合國邀請不同國家關注香港，慘吃閉門羹...<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部一直擔心讓BNO移英會違反《中英聯合聲明》，最終靠一封信件開了綠燈...<br />\n<br />\nAileen指，以往港人被外國認定經濟掛帥，追捧中環價值；反修例運動後，外國欣賞香港年輕人勇敢爭取自由、民主、公義...<br />\n<br />\n她呼籲移民港人在異鄉要積極融入社會，更要參政：「你起碼要投票，日後可以去做區議員，好似加拿大有好多香港人做區議員，現在有人做國會議員，為香港族群喺外面為香港發聲，唔可以圍埋喺China Town、Hong Kong Town ，否則你唔會有任何力量。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/ZT6IWZ6F6JBF7FICNFW4G3IZNU/?fbclid=IwAR1rTGoXN_W_3cYAGuPrVlEHkDJYywuoqkUgGN-UkCv12u9iVfaIt1uGJ-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FZT6IWZ6F6JBF7FICNFW4G3IZNU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1rTGoXN_W_3cYAGuPrVlEHkDJYywuoqkUgGN-UkCv12u9iVfaIt1uGJ-0&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=d1a444b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FZT6IWZ6F6JBF7FICNFW4G3IZNU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1rTGoXN_W_3cYAGuPrVlEHkDJYywuoqkUgGN-UkCv12u9iVfaIt1uGJ-0&h=b9f62f88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/ZT6IWZ6F6JBF7FICNFW4G3IZNU/?fbclid=IwAR1rTGoXN_W_3cYAGuPrVlEHkDJYywuoqkUgGN-UkCv12u9iVfaIt1uGJ-0</a>"},{"pid":"44e309faa1161aa1c62fab47e0978d15483c2721","tid":2420933,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"722198e2464729454e20326445477b688eef025d","tid":2420933,"uid":91721,"lik